{"tid":2173563,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《飛天小女警》將推出真人版劇集　主角三人長大棄做女警","createTime":"2020-08-25T10:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T04:37:12.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0fa10603d83d247021e35e66be10ba111f3fa2","tid":2173563,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:17:19.000Z","msg":"根據外媒報導，華納兄弟旗下的 CW 電視將推出《飛天小女警》真人版作品，但目前尚未確認推出時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《飛天小女警》自 1998 年播出，截至 2005 年共推出 6 季（共 78 集）的電視動畫、三部特別篇、還有 2002 年的動畫電影《飛天小女警大電影》，而早在 2016 年也曾推出動畫重啟版，及日本動畫版。<br />\n<br />\n而報導在今次真人版的劇情：三個主角花花、泡泡和毛毛已經不再是當年的小女孩，現在她們已經成為二十多歲的大人，並且她們對於過去竟將自己的童年時光都花在對抗壞人、打擊犯罪上感到不開心。然而當世界比過去更需要她們的此刻，她們能夠再次齊聚拯救世界嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gank.fanpiece.com/m/gamelife/c1383413.html?fbclid=IwAR3z1Yt5PRS-JmXaRT6EmRBBOh6CHDjRE3Vl4gUjUURVpvJ2Qn8vhsSpqRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgank.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fgamelife%2Fc1383413.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3z1Yt5PRS-JmXaRT6EmRBBOh6CHDjRE3Vl4gUjUURVpvJ2Qn8vhsSpqRs&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3febbc7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://gank.fanpiece.com/m/gamelife/c1383413.html?fbclid=IwAR3z1Yt5PRS-JmXaRT6EmRBBOh6CHDjRE3Vl4gUjUURVpvJ2Qn8vhsSpqRs</a>"},{"pid":"2afcc127841ef3dcdb545d707980dbaeb28c633d","tid":2173563,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"做電子雞 被人進去"},{"pid":"eed06d47db237a91eab6e0c1b86cad9b112d5b66","tid":2173563,"uid":122798,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"等睇全部主角都係黑妹"},{"pid":"4eb4abbd189f707a3d5c172ca568867e73fe72a0","tid":2173563,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:29:41.000Z","msg":"通天女公安"},{"pid":"b7282d5399fa42c352bee712b96ae248c570d50f","tid":2173563,"uid":10757,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"一個亞洲人，一個黑人，一個變性人 迪士尼開戲 票房Gogogo"},{"pid":"f81bb8708d9c0d6798c88e8a7